# Post-Edit Verification

After editing any `.vue` or `.ts` file in `app/`:

1. Run **`npm run check`** — runs typecheck, lint, and format check in one go.
2. If something fails, fix it. Use **`npm run check:fix`** to auto-fix lint and format where possible.
3. Do not consider the task complete until `npm run check` passes.

For Vue components: follow vue-code-quality rule and use Nuxt MCP docs when unsure about best practices.
